BAB III Diagram and Design Requirements

Project Context

Project title:

Perancangan Sistem Informasi Pemesanan Bunga Berbasis Web pada Usaha Florist Little Joy Jakarta

Technology stack:

* Laravel
* React
* TypeScript
* Inertia.js
* Tailwind CSS
* MySQL
* phpMyAdmin

User roles:

* Guest
* Customer
* Operator
* Admin

The application contains:

* authentication;
* product catalogue;
* category management;
* product management;
* inventory management;
* shopping cart;
* checkout;
* manual bank-transfer payment;
* payment-proof upload;
* payment verification;
* order-status management;
* order-status history;
* customer management;
* operator management;
* dashboard;
* sales reports.

Main Objective

Produce diagrams and visual design artefacts for BAB III of the thesis.

All diagrams must be based on:

1. the approved product requirements;
2. the actual application workflow;
3. the current database design;
4. the actual roles and permissions;
5. the existing or planned source-code structure.

Do not invent modules, actors, tables, or processes outside the documented project scope.

